name: MyPlace Leisure Home @ Santo Domingo - 3 Nights #1
description:
A recently renovated classic building with a large roof garden overlooking dozens of domes and beautiful sunsets. The building has a gym, laundry room, and a grill at the roof garden

Great accommodation for couples, adventurers, and families with children. ThereÂ´s a very comfortable queen-size bed, a sofa-bed, large bathroom, equipped kitchen and dining table, mini-fridge, microwave, oven, and Smart TV.

1BR unit Max occupancy 4.Private 2 have 1 queen-size bed, 1 sofa bed, partial kitchen, and 1 bath. Suitable for 2 adults and 2 children under 12yrs old.

1Bedroom units do not have a private bedroom.

Enjoy Downtown Mexico City inside and out of the apartment. Feel the 19th Century Mexico atmosphere with the Colonial surroundings and also the retro-cool decor that transports you to another time.

No Pets. Please contact the resort directly regarding its ADA/general service animal policy.

name: Myplace Leisure Home @ Donceles - 3 Nights #1
description:
A recently renovated historic building with a relaxing roof garden equipped with a grill, a gym, a laundry room, and a lot of charm.

Fully equipped bedroom loft with one queen bed and a very functional sofa bed that transforms either in two twins or one queen-size bed. TV with Netflix and Sat Tv, Bluetooth speaker with CD and AM and FM radio, a well-equipped kitchen and dining table, high-speed internet 30 Mbps, a big safe that can fit your laptop and access to the buildings common areas such as the gym, the terrace, the grill and the laundry room with a washer and a dryer.

Enjoy Mexico City from within the core location of the most amazing and important cultural, traditional touristic places. While you rest in a kind one-bedroom apartment in a newly refurbished old Downtown classic building located at the corner of Donceles and Cajon del 54, just behind the National Art Museum and only one block away from Bellas Artes.

Additional rules and notices
